## Key Discoveries This Session
1. max_steps = 10000 in tournament (previous tests used 5000)
2. Economy collapse in 2nd half (steps 5000-10000) is the #1 score killer
3. num_agents bug helps for max pressure but causes 0 miners in small teams
4. Capping budget by team_size guarantees economy sustainability
5. Score = avg(net_junction_count) per tick, normalized by max_steps
6. Scrambling IS essential (SustainV3 without scrambling: 2.77 vs 8.67 with)
7. Map variance is huge (1.57-8.72 across seeds)
